 DIN Offc Pro&quot;,sans-serif\">st</span></sup><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Unilever DIN Offc Pro&quot;,sans-serif\"> March 2026 in accordance with Company Act 2063, section 90(2), 90(3), 96(1) and Article </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;</span>61.1,69 and 77 of the Articles of Association of the Company.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Unilever DIN Offc Pro&quot;,sans-serif\">Kindly take the above information on record.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0in\" class=\"MsoNormal\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0in\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Unilever DIN Offc Pro&quot;,sans-serif\">For Unilever Nepal Limited</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0in\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Unilever DIN Offc Pro&quot;,sans-serif\">Govinda Bahadur Shahi</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0in\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Unilever DIN Offc Pro&quot;,sans-serif\">Company Secretary</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Unilever DIN Offc Pro&quot;,sans-serif\">CC:</span></b></p><p style=\"margin-left:.25in;mso-add-space:auto;\ntext-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\" class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">-</span><span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Unilever DIN Offc Pro&quot;,sans-serif\">Office of the Company Registrar, Tripureshwor, Kathmandu</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:.25in;mso-add-space:\nauto;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\" class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">-</span><span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Unilever DIN Offc Pro&quot;,sans-serif\">Securities Exc